RBAC permissions UI installed!

Usage:
import { RbacPermissions } from '@/components/auth-rbac-permissions'

<RbacPermissions
  permissions={[{ id: 'users.create', label: 'Create users', group: 'Users' }]}
  roles={[{ id: 'admin', name: 'Admin', permissions: ['users.create'] }]}
  onTogglePermission={async (roleId, permId, granted) => { /* persist */ }}
/>

Requires shadcn/ui: npx shadcn@latest add button input card label checkbox dialog tooltip
